---
// Slide1
---
<section class="slide-container slide-title active">
      <span class="slide-number">01 / 16</span>
      <div class="title-icon">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i>
      </div>
      <h1>Сайт за один урок.<br><span class="gradient-blue">С помощью ИИ.</span></h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Без кода. Без опыта. Без долгого обучения.</p>
      <div class="title-tags">
        <span class="title-tag blue"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i> Быстро</span>
        <span class="title-tag green"><i class="fa-solid fa-robot"></i> С помощью ИИ</span>
        <span class="title-tag gold"><i class="fa-solid fa-sack-dollar"></i> Практично</span>
      </div>
    </section>

<style is:global>
/* Slide 1 — Title */
.slide-title {
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  background: #ffffff;
}

.slide-title .title-icon {
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #ec4899 100%);
  border-radius: 22px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.25);
  animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.slide-title .title-icon i {
  font-size: 38px;
  color: #ffffff;
}

@keyframes float {

  0%,
  100% {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  50% {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
  }
}

.slide-title h1 {
  font-size: 2.8rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #1e293b;
  line-height: 1.2;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

.slide-title h1 .gradient-blue {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #ec4899 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  animation: hueShift 5s infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes hueShift {
  0% {
    filter: hue-rotate(0deg);
  }

  100% {
    filter: hue-rotate(30deg);
  }
}

.slide-title .subtitle {
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  color: #64748b;
  max-width: 500px;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.slide-title .title-tags {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 12px;
  justify-content: center;
}

.slide-title .title-tag {
  background: #f8fafc;
  border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 10px 22px;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: #475569;
  font-weight: 600;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

.slide-title .title-tag i {
  font-size: 15px;
}

.slide-title .title-tag.blue i {
  color: #2563eb;
}

.slide-title .title-tag.green i {
  color: #16a34a;
}

.slide-title .title-tag.gold i {
  color: #d97706;
}

/* Common headings */
h2 {
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #0f172a;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

h2 i {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #ec4899 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
}
</style>
